# DevForge v9.0 — 43-module web app → builds to single HTML (~980KB / 1200KB limit)

## Build: `node build.js` (produces devforge-v9.html)
## Test: `npm test` (197 tests, all passing)
## Verify: `npm run check`

## Rules
1. Edit source in src/ — never edit devforge-v9.html directly
2. Never use ${expr} inside single-quoted strings
3. Gen files: `const G = S.genLang==='ja';` at function start
4. UI text: `S.lang` + `t('key')` or ternary
5. TechDB req: use English codes + reqLabel() for display
6. CSS: use custom properties (--accent, --bg-2, --text, etc.)
7. State: `save()` after S mutations
8. getEntityColumns: always pass 3rd arg `knownEntities`
9. ENTITY_METHODS: REST API methods are entity-specific (common.js)
10. After edits: `npm test && node build.js`

## Key Files
- src/generators/common.js — ENTITY_COLUMNS (145+), ENTITY_METHODS, FEATURE_DETAILS (31), detectDomain() (24 domains)
- src/generators/p1-sdd.js — Specification/constitution/technical-plan/tasks/verification
- src/generators/p2-devcontainer.js — DevContainer, Dockerfile, docker-compose, post-create
- src/generators/p3-mcp.js — MCP servers (backend/domain-specific)
- src/generators/p4-airules.js — CLAUDE.md, AI_BRIEF.md, .cursorrules, AGENTS.md, skills/
- src/generators/p5-quality.js — QA blueprint, test matrix, incident response
- src/generators/p10-reverse.js — Reverse engineering, goal decomposition, REVERSE_FLOW_MAP
- src/generators/p11-implguide.js — Implementation playbook, AI dev runbook
- src/data/presets.js — 41 project presets (LMS, EC, SaaS, CRM, etc.)
- src/data/compat-rules.js — 45 compatibility validation rules
- test/ — 197 tests (run `npm test` before committing)

## For comprehensive guidance, see CLAUDE.md (1000+ lines, includes bug patterns, security best practices, size budget management)
